Olympic Village\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali's heavyweight bout\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the 25-year-old did receive some help from Papua New Guinea's boxing coach Peter Morrison, he was beaten handily by Schelstraete, who left the Samoan bleeding from the cheek.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Papua_New_Guinea\", \"score\": 0.582283679898821, \"rank\": 0.5889216176202127, \"text\": \"Papua New Guinea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Papua_New_Guinea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Papua_New_Guinea\"}, {\"begin\": 826, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Morrison\", \"score\": 0.9999999865933661, \"rank\": 7.094173477633044e-09, \"text\": \"Peter Morrison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Morrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Morrison\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"score\": 0.9974935142318698, \"rank\": 0.001760911363077064, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some help\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"Schelstraete\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheek\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was thinking about pulling out \\u2026 it's been hard,\\\" Pacific Games champion Plodzicki-Faoagali said.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pacific Games champion Plodzicki-Faoagali\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been hard to stay strong.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been struggling mentally the past few days.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought I was going to win a medal for sure, but it's been really hard mentally.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not care about the medal right now.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even through these hard times, I appreciate everyone.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these hard times\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to come back stronger and chase my dreams.\\\"\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dreams\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schelstraete, who spoke to Plodzicki-Faoagali before and after the fight and held up his opponent's arm in the ring, said the Samoan had displayed great spirit just by showing up.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"score\": 0.9974935142318698, \"rank\": 0.001760911363077064, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schelstraete\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"his opponent's arm\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"great spirit\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Big respect to him.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Big respect\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's got a big heart.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big heart\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He honored his coach by fighting,\\\" Schelstraete said.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"Schelstraete\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These coaches, they are very selfless.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They put in all their work for us to get here, and for him to not be here to experience that moment, it's very sad.\\\"\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all their work\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if it was hard to fight in the bout, Schelstraete said: \\\"I had to put that aside.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"Schelstraete\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I felt genuinely sorry for him.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you have to put the emotions aside.\\\"\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schelstraete meets Spain's Enmanuel Reyes on Thursday.- Rappler.com How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5